{"tid":2270329,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"散戶：質疑證監及港交所對螞蟻問題是否早已知情","createTime":"2020-11-04T03:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T05:13:31.000Z","uid":21470,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"865a3080365994c43b1a9418e67c88ded088a3be","tid":2270329,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T03:52:15.000Z","msg":"有散戶對螞蟻暫緩上市感失望 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n螞蟻集團暫緩上市計劃，散戶何小姐指，對螞蟻暫緩上市感到十分失望，指幸好沒有借孖展認購，認為借孖展認購的散戶蒙受巨大損失。她認為，證監會及港交所需為投資者蒙受損失，負上重大責任，認為證監會及港交所一早已知情螞蟻將暫緩上市，對投資者十分不公平。 <br />\n<br />\n蘇小姐亦對螞蟻暫緩上市感到失望，形容情況是得而復失，但不會影響她對集團的信心。她又指，認購螞蟻新股是追趕市場熱潮，但iBond是同期推出，對沒有抽iBond而抽螞蟻感到後悔。散戶澤小姐指，未有敢到失望，但不知道為何暫緩上市，若螞蟻重新上市，亦會再認購。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2364641\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2364641&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3Vcyjbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBIbvNjo%3D&h=32f48dda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2364641</a>"},{"pid":"86d0c02a4dadffd63934ebbdcb90b9501cc51011","tid":2270329,"uid":24660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T03:55:00.000Z","msg":"對沒有抽iBond而抽螞蟻感到後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\niBond都未截喎，仲抽得"},{"pid":"9e44371cc58ed2258a77940a5763d4ccec91dc59","tid":2270329,"uid":51920,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:06:14.000Z","msg":"媽咪面早已知情"},{"pid":"8b569aa92667553dc222c449015d1a11a54f8b20","tid":2270329,"uid":142574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86d0c02a4dadffd63934ebbdcb90b9501cc51011","tid":2270329,"uid":24660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T03:55:00.000Z","msg":"對沒有抽iBond而抽螞蟻感到後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /